        "text_GWK7gK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>All parties submitting vulnerability reports are expected to: </p><ol><li>Comply with all applicable laws and regulations. </li><li>Base all reports on the latest released firmware. </li><li>Use the dedicated channel (<a href=\"mailto:support@hypershop.com\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">support@hypershop.com</span></a>) for submitting reports. </li><li>Adhere to data protection best practices and avoid actions that compromise the privacy or security of Hyper’s users, employees, agents, services, or systems. </li><li>Refrain from disclosing any information about the vulnerability to third parties prior to an agreed-upon disclosure date. </li></ol><p>Please note that Hyper does not operate a vulnerability bounty program at this time. </p>",
